Interface VersionedObject<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CheckboxModel, RangedValueModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultCheckboxModel, DefaultRangedValueModel, DocumentModel, RollupPanel.OpenCheckboxModel, VersionedHolder

    public interface VersionedObject<T>
    Implemented by objects that provided a versioned view of a value. Callers can create VersionedReferences and then easily detect when the value has changed.
